oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Grand Ole Opry - Prince Albert - 1960-08-13 - Part 2
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Part 2 of Prince Albert tobacco sponsored Grand Ole Opry segment from August 13, 1960. Featuring Grant Turner (announcer), the Wilburn Brothers (host/performer), guest performer Charlie Walker, and regular performers Archie Campbell, Tommy Vaden, the Jordanaires, Chet Atkins, June Carter, and Del Wood. Held at Ryman Auditorium, Nashville, TN. It is announced that this is the 1088th broadcast.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:creator: June Carter; Archie Campbell; Ferlin Husky; Charlie Walker; Del Wood; Jordanaires; Wilburn Brothers
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dcterms:tableOfContents: The Wilburn Brothers introduce June Carter -- Comedy routine (June Carter, Archie Campbell) -- The Proof Is In The Puffing (Ferlin Husky) (recording) -- Grant Turner introduces Charlie Walker -- Pick Me Up On Your Way Down (Charlie Walker) -- The Wilburn Brothers introduce Del Wood -- Bye Bye Blackbird (Del Wood, Jordanaires) -- Grant Turner introduces the Wilburn Brothers -- Somebody's Back In Town (Wilburn Brothers) -- Closing theme -- Closing statement (Wilburn Brothers) -- Camel Cigarettes commercial -- Network announcements
